flowchart TB
    subgraph ingest [Ingest]
        SRC[Source Adapter]
        TGT[Target Adapter]
    end

    SRC --> S1[Stage 1: Schema Validation]
    TGT --> S1
    S1 --> S2[Stage 2: Row Count]
    S2 --> CAN[Canonicalization Engine]
    CAN --> S3[Stage 3: Partition Fingerprints]
    S3 --> S4[Stage 4: Bucket Compare]
    S4 -->|match| DONE[Report OK]
    S4 -->|mismatch| S5[Stage 5: Row Fingerprints]
    S5 --> S6[Stage 6: Column Drilldown]
    S6 --> RPT[VALIDATION_RESULTS.md]

    subgraph pushdown [Compute Near Data]
        SQL[Warehouse SQL GROUP BY partition_id]
        SCAN[File streaming scan]
    end

    SQL -.-> S3
    SCAN -.-> S3
